title: How to Master Public Speaking
itunes:title: How to Master Public Speaking
description:
Episode 529 - The #1 fear in the world is speaking in front of other people, but every time we speak we are speaking to others. So, shouldn't we all want to learn how to become better speakers? In this episode, I have the #1 rated college speaker in the world giving you tips on how to improve your speaking skills!
